---
import home from '../images/home.png'
---

<div class="relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div
      class="z-10 relative pb-8 sm:pb-16 md:pb-20 lg:max-w-2xl lg:w-full lg:pb-28 xl:pb-32 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"
    >
      <svg
        class="hidden lg:block absolute right-0 inset-y-0 h-full w-48 text-white dark:text-gray-900 transform translate-x-1/2"
        fill="currentColor"
        viewBox="0 0 100 100"
        preserveAspectRatio="none"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        <polygon points="50,0 100,0 50,100 0,100"></polygon>
      </svg>
      <main
        class="pt-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:pt-12 sm:px-6 md:pt-16 lg:pt-20 lg:px-8 xl:pt-28"
      >
        <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
          <h1
            class="text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl text-left"
          >
            <span class="block xl:inline">Blue Partners is the</span>{' '}
            <span class="block text-indigo-800 dark:text-purple-300 xl:inline"
              >tech headhunting
            </span>
            <span class="block xl:inline"> company 2.0</span>
          </h1>
          <p
            class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0"
          >
          The epic of our company is based on the need of change and the need of continuos improvement on performance. We decided to start the partnership quitting from Big Multinational Companies in which we were feeling static and unempowered.
          </p>
          <p
            class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0"
          >
          Blue Partners processes are light, fast, dynamic and totally customizable.
          </p>
          <p
            class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0"
          >
          We want to follow our client companies in their growth by providing a quality driven selection of the profiles they need. We believe that is time to change the headhunting world and we have the attitude for doing it.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-5 sm:mt-8 sm:flex sm:justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <div class="rounded-md shadow">
              <a
                href="/about"
                class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-indigo-800 hover:bg-pink-600 dark:text-black dark:bg-purple-300 dark:hover:bg-pink-300 md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10"
              >
                Contact us
              </a>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:right-0 lg:w-1/2 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-500"
  >
    <img
      class="h-56 w-full object-cover sm:h-72 md:h-96 lg:w-full lg:h-full"
      src={home}
      alt="featured"
    />
  </div>
</div>